trans-unit.source: Represents the schema of an enumeration property.

This class inherits the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty.Default%2A> property from the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty> class, which has no meaning for this class.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen arver <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty.Default%2A>egenskapen fra <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty>klassen som har ingen betydning for denne klassen.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty> </xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.BaseProperty.Default%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.IsDefault%2A> property on the <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue> instead to mark the default value for this property.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.IsDefault%2A>egenskap i den <xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue>i stedet å merke standardverdien for denne egenskapen.</xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue> </xref:Microsoft.Build.Framework.XamlTypes.EnumValue.IsDefault%2A>

trans-unit.source: The default constructor for a dynamic enum property.
Gets or sets the provider that produces the list of possible values for this property.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir leverandøren som produserer listen over mulige verdier for denne egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: This property must be set during deserialization.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen må angis under deserialisering.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a provider-specific set of options to pass to the provider.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et leverandørspesifikk sett med alternativer for å sende til leverandøren.
